thread.title: First time user
thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by First time user

author: First time user
title: First time user
text: The whole process was very efficient, from the initial enquiry at the local branch, the on-line process for setting up the transfer of five packages from Perth to Melbourne, the receipt of the goods and the tracking service provided (supplemented by that of the carrier). The goods arrived at the destination on the day predicted.
